## Technical Implementation

### 1. VARK Quiz Component (FlutterFlow)

```dart
// Custom Function: Calculate VARK Score
Map<String, double> calculateVARKScore(List<String> answers) {
  Map<String, double> scores = {
    'visual': 0,
    'aural': 0,
    'readWrite': 0,
    'kinesthetic': 0
  };
  
  // Process each answer
  for (String answer in answers) {
    switch (answer) {
      case 'V':
        scores['visual']++;
        break;
      case 'A':
        scores['aural']++;
        break;
      case 'R':
        scores['readWrite']++;
        break;
      case 'K':
        scores['kinesthetic']++;
        break;
    }
  }
  
  // Calculate percentages
  int totalAnswers = answers.length;
  scores.forEach((key, value) {
    scores[key] = (value / totalAnswers) * 100;
  });
  
  return scores;
}
```

### 2. Content Filtering Logic

```dart
// Custom Function: Filter Modules by VARK
List<Module> filterModulesByVARK(
  List<Module> allModules,
  Map<String, dynamic> userVarkPrefs
) {
  String dominantStyle = userVarkPrefs['dominantStyle'];
  
  // Sort modules by VARK relevance
  return allModules.where((module) {
    return module.varkTags.contains(dominantStyle);
  }).toList()
  ..sort((a, b) {
    // Prioritize modules where primaryVarkStyle matches user's dominant style
    if (a.primaryVarkStyle == dominantStyle) return -1;
    if (b.primaryVarkStyle == dominantStyle) return 1;
    return 0;
  });
}
```

