### Content Creation Guidelines

#### Visual Content Requirements
- 3-5 minute video modules
- Infographic summaries
- Animated demonstrations
- Color-coded progress tracking
- Visual metaphors (e.g., "focus laser")

#### Auditory Content Requirements
- 5-10 minute audio guides
- Background music/sounds optional
- Clear verbal instructions
- Rhythmic elements for memorization
- Voice tone: calm, confident, rhythmic

#### Read/Write Content Requirements
- 500-1000 word articles
- Bulleted lists and numbered steps
- Downloadable PDF summaries
- Interactive worksheets
- Journal prompt templates

#### Kinesthetic Content Requirements
- Step-by-step physical exercises
- "Try this now" prompts
- Practice duration estimates
- Physical cue descriptions
- Movement-based metaphors

