## AI Integration & Adaptive Delivery

### 1. Prompt Engineering for VARK

```javascript
// Cloud Function: Generate VARK-Adapted AI Insight
const generateVARKAdaptedInsight = (userData, insightData) => {
  const varkPromptAdditions = {
    visual: `
      Use visual metaphors and imagery in your response.
      Include phrases like "picture this", "visualize", "imagine".
      Suggest visual techniques and mental imagery exercises.
      Format with clear visual breaks and structure.
    `,
    aural: `
      Use auditory language and sound-based metaphors.
      Include phrases like "listen to", "hear", "sound of".
      Suggest verbal cues and rhythmic techniques.
      Write as if speaking directly to the user.
    `,
    readWrite: `
      Use clear, structured writing with lists and steps.
      Include phrases like "write down", "note that", "list out".
      Suggest journaling exercises and written reflection.
      Provide templates or frameworks they can fill in.
    `,
    kinesthetic: `
      Use physical and sensory language.
      Include phrases like "feel", "experience", "practice".
      Suggest physical drills and body-awareness exercises.
      Focus on action-oriented advice.
    `
  };
  
  const systemPrompt = `
    ${baseSystemPrompt}
    
    CRITICAL: This user's dominant learning style is ${userData.varkPreferences.dominantStyle}.
    ${varkPromptAdditions[userData.varkPreferences.dominantStyle]}
    
    Adapt all recommendations and language to match this learning preference.
  `;
  
  return callOpenAI(systemPrompt, insightData);
};
```

