## UI/UX Adaptations

### 1. Module Display Cards

```dart
// VARK-Specific Module Card Designs
Widget buildVARKModuleCard(Module module, String userVarkStyle) {
  switch (userVarkStyle) {
    case 'visual':
      return VisualModuleCard(
        thumbnail: module.thumbnailUrl,
        playIcon: Icons.play_circle_filled,
        duration: module.duration,
        visualIndicator: LinearProgressIndicator()
      );
      
    case 'aural':
      return AuralModuleCard(
        waveformImage: module.waveformUrl,
        speakerIcon: Icons.volume_up,
        duration: module.duration,
        audioQualityBadge: true
      );
      
    case 'readWrite':
      return ReadWriteModuleCard(
        excerptText: module.excerpt,
        wordCount: module.wordCount,
        downloadIcon: Icons.download,
        bookmarkOption: true
      );
      
    case 'kinesthetic':
      return KinestheticModuleCard(
        actionImage: module.actionImageUrl,
        practiceTime: module.practiceMinutes,
        interactiveBadge: true,
        tryNowButton: true
      );
  }
}
```

